    A[Start] --> B(Inspect physical disc surface)
    B --> C(Insert DVD and Open VLC Media Player to verify playback)
    C --> D{Playback Stutters?}
    D -->|Yes| C
    D -->|No| E(Proceed with Handbrake)

    E --> F(Open Handbrake)
    F --> G(Click Open Source to load the disc)
    G --> H(Select the main movie title)
    H --> I(Apply the Fast 480p30 preset)
    I --> J(Set the Container to MP4)
    J --> K(Enable the Deinterlace filter)
    K --> L(Type the file name)
    L --> M{Disk Full Error?}
    M -->|Yes| N(Purge previous temporary files in staging area)
    N --> G
    M -->|No| O(Handbrake Encoding Complete)

    O --> P(Drag and Drop MP4 file to client USB drive)
    P --> Q{File over 4GB fails to transfer?}
    Q -->|Yes| R(Reformat USB drive to exFAT)
    R --> P
    Q -->|No| S(MP4 successfully transferred)

    S --> T(Right-Click the USB drive icon and Select Eject)
    T --> U(Return the physical disc and USB to the client)
    U --> V[End]